{"tid":1025450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[短命Post] 賭盤過三關 | 「唔識唔買」「長賭輸水」","createTime":"2019-02-17T10:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T13:02:45.000Z","uid":29006,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea377063f7bd6340de7a67d7d254dabc7888ff69","tid":1025450,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"「唔識唔買」：好多長期賭徒會平注日日買波，即使一啲唔識、無睇嘅賽事都會求其買下，呢度只會買英超、西甲、歐聯，對隊波有了解先會落注。<br />\n<br />\n「長賭輸水」：就算你跟唔跟呢度買都好，都想奉勸喺馬會賭波嘅賭仔只買盤，唔買其他。因為盤嘅水份抽得最少，馬會優勢8%，比起大細、角球等15%少，所以唔好買盤以外嘅項目。<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講，第一關 皇馬-2/2.5 @2.05<br />\n<br />\n過個三關，贏錢全推，玩完cash out 請屋企人食飯，長賭輸水，切記。"},{"pid":"bbfe57472fa9fa00776549b03c5b1813c81bcc57","tid":1025450,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"1:0"},{"pid":"fb9ee9e3cf3d9cbdb8f674c5880cfcf3cbefcf63","tid":1025450,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"買左對家 希望無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466fc9bd20ec7bf1ca61b2256d4d1f7a91672fa2","tid":1025450,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9ee9e3cf3d9cbdb8f674c5880cfcf3cbefcf63","tid":1025450,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"買左對家 希望無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"其實無所謂，成個post 重點係嗰阿媽係女人喺投注技巧，Follow 到就好，加油"},{"pid":"803048a8dfc7dabf06c61c09e6d225f08d46b3f9","tid":1025450,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"1:1"},{"pid":"d32cbd12c2d4790f67816afdc7f455051a05da33","tid":1025450,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"1:2"},{"pid":"c03c3a726206a12ffbcd63c28b0a590fdb6bfe2a","tid":1025450,"uid":29006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:37:12.